The First Fully Permissionless, User-Owned Launchpad

FEY Protocol is built on Base and redistributes 100% of protocol fees to token stakers. Unlike traditional launchpads owned by corporations, FEY operates as decentralized public infrastructure where users gain real ownership through staking.

Core Features

  • 100% Fee Redistribution: All protocol fees automatically flow back to stakers
  • Permissionless Operations: No governance required for core protocol functions
  • Creator Rewards: Token deployers earn fees in $FEY for successful launches
  • Automatic Buybacks: WETH fees trigger $FEY buybacks every 60 seconds
  • TOKEN/FEY Pairing: All tokens pair with $FEY, creating constant buy pressure
